  <brief_title>An Evaluation of Integration Success and Maintenance of Short Implants in Maxillas Needing Sinus Augmentation</brief_title>
  <acronym>Romeo</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Multicenter, Randomized Multicenter Study of Short Implants Used to Obviate the Need for Sinus Augmentation: an Assessment of Clinical Outcomes and Resource Allocation.</official_title>
